  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7787142">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7787142/" class="title-link">站在旁观者的角度看别处的战争</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7787142"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/46191599/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u46191599-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/46191599/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">抱字</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-02-24"
      class="main-meta">2016-02-24 00:01:15</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7787142_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                   太平洋战争发生在中国抗日战争同期，但是由于对战的双方不再有中国参加，因此站在旁观者角度来看太平洋战争反而比抗日战争更能引起一些思考。 首先，读史需要时刻记住一种代入感才可能拨开云雾找到当时人物的真实心理情况。 初看本书时，对于前期日军在太平洋战场上痛击美军，...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7787142_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7787142_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










